Hotel

agents: HotelRobot, guest
locations: lobby, room
resources: storageBox, items

HotelRobot:
	1-5: moveTo lobby
	6: fetch items
	7: moveTo room
	8: follow guest
	9: fetch storageBox
	10: deliver items

Lobby

agents: HotelRobot
locations: lobby
resources: none

Room

agents: Human
locations: room
resources: none

Butler:
	1-5: moveTo lobby
	6: fetch items
	7: moveTo room
	8: follow guest
	9: fetch storageBox
	10: deliver items

Lift:
	1-3: moveTo lobby
	4: moveTo room

Items:
	1-10: deposit storageBox
	11: moveTo deliveryLocation

Presence:
	1-5: moveTo lobby
	6: follow guest

Access:
	1-5: moveTo storageBox
	6: fetch storageBox

Delivery:
	1-3: moveTo deliveryLocation
	4: deliver items
